        <updateDate>2019-09-18T19:31:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Leniency for Terrorists Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill makes certain federal prisoners ineligible to receive good time credit. </p> <p>Specifically, it prohibits good time credit for a federal prisoner who is serving time for a terrorism offense. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
